{
  "stem": "5891.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I probably had it for about five or six months, and then none no more.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not a nice thing to say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not a nice thing to say at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was under-- we had, like, they gave you, like, an undergarment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did give you pants, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, you know, people, they stole little things in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You lost things.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For desperation, it's not really stealing because you're desperate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People are desperate, OK?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So sometimes you lost your underwear if you didn't lay on it at night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, when you want to rinse it out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to rinse my stuff out a little bit, with sand, in the wash bin, long thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I'd wash them out a little bit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I rolled it in my dress, the damp, and I put it underneath where I laid.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then it was dry in the morning when I got up, before I had to go out for work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because that's the only way you could survive a little bit for your cleanliness.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That don't mean you didn't get the dry [? rot. ?] I had it, too, but I-- that's how we did it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You learned little tricks for the survival there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If something was a little damp yet, but was a little bit clean.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, took the underwear, that slip, and we ripped it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We made little rags, and guarded those little rags like they were gold, those little rags.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And rinsed them out a little bit in that sand thing, and put them under the mattress and dried them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then nobody else steal the little rags from you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because you couldn't even find rags, because you'd need them for, for looking for your feet, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
